{"tid":1048374,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"主子嬲左我定真係性格如此？","createTime":"2019-03-05T15:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T14:50:20.000Z","uid":42449,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8e07cf68e99a6d0ccd819a65bed1c5ff3af103bc","tid":1048374,"uid":42449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:09:46.000Z","msg":"(借人acc) <br />\n<br />\n我係新手貓奴，想問問各位巴絲。<br />\n<br />\n我隻布偶仔1歲，岩岩入屋1 星期多d。入屋第一日，好快出籠，好痴我同我老公，成日跟出，無論肚餓與否，食飽有幾眼訓，叫親佢個名都會衝埋黎俾我地摸，頭頂我地手，反肚，仲咕嚕咕嚕聲。<br />\n<br />\n但過多日，因為幫佢轉糧，佢有少少軟便，腳仔，pat pat 毛都hi 到屎，所以要捉住佢抹濕tissue, 搞到佢唔鍾意。<br />\n<br />\n而且前主人放長糧，我同我老公都怕佢食到好肥，所以無論佢點叫，我地都跟糧袋個份糧多少少咁食，唔知佢係咪又唔鐘意<br />\n<br />\n三黎，我老公唔想太寵隻仔，有d 指令eg 唔可以入禁區，佢教佢時可能有d 惡同大聲，<br />\n<br />\n而家隻仔除左食野叫我地餵 or 眼訓時俾我地任人魚肉摸，其他時間都唔多痴我地，已經出動左零食同貓棒同佢玩，但玩完食完又我行我素，有時叫都扮聽唔到。<br />\n<br />\n請問各位，呢個情況係本身隻仔性格唔痴人，定係嬲左我地？如果嬲，有無辦法好返？我地都想佢痴我地多d"},{"pid":"a12d412849fc0a233baad35319057b9d9b5886af","tid":1048374,"uid":50658,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:12:20.000Z","msg":"要放咗圖先會有人答"},{"pid":"a78456df1e692a49dc102e139730ead636c3596f","tid":1048374,"uid":170019,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:17:09.000Z","msg":"妳想聽聽話話痴妳既應該養狗"},{"pid":"410b34e095ab776e0267e8eba1d4d9f198a025db","tid":1048374,"uid":187363,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:21:16.000Z","msg":"放過佢啦<br />\n你想養嗰種動物係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68ec8dab040aad8d95f5dc5b91f3bb3db834269","tid":1048374,"uid":48572,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:23:00.000Z","msg":"其實你地要既係狗而唔係貓"},{"pid":"87786853f102fc07b3112325cb7a423458649da8","tid":1048374,"uid":194298,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:25:02.000Z","msg":"高斗貓，未聽過？<br />\n10隻有8隻都係唔睬人架啦"},{"pid":"50d16a40a70105b5099bc22e05c73dc173b67d7f","tid":1048374,"uid":188310,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:25:45.000Z","msg":"佢高傲，但宅心仁厚"},{"pid":"e9a11842172938f169f4b29da17bc88273905813","tid":1048374,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:27:18.000Z","msg":"冇圖點討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b5b25faee645ac4fe96048bfe200a9cac6be2a","tid":1048374,"uid":152209,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"410b34e095ab776e0267e8eba1d4d9f198a025db","tid":1048374,"uid":187363,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:21:16.000Z","msg":"放過佢啦<br />\n你想養嗰種動物係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:27:30.000Z","msg":"岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你想玩控制同命令 唔該養狗"},{"pid":"6e87d86a13d1cc586fcbc08ad332d53a70deea9f","tid":1048374,"uid":152209,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"b0b5b25faee645ac4fe96048bfe200a9cac6be2a","tid":1048374,"uid":152209,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"410b34e095ab776e0267e8eba1d4d9f198a025db","tid":1048374,"uid":187363,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:21:16.000Z","msg":"放過佢啦<br />\n你想養嗰種動物係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:27:30.000Z","msg":"岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你想玩控制同命令 唔該養狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:29:20.000Z","msg":"養猫同養港女一樣唔可以屌同大聲講要慢教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n養狗算啦你地"},{"pid":"d2447d6017182aacde340b3fc93d3b66aeacbaa0","tid":1048374,"uid":11774,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:37:09.000Z","msg":"貓嘅性格一向都係咁 愛理不理<br />\n佢想玩 自然會搵你；佢唔想 你點引佢都無用<br />\n你兩公婆唔應該養貓 應該養狗<br />\n狗比較符合你哋想要嘅要求<br />\n好多人貪貓方便 唔洗每日出街散步<br />\n擺喺屋企就得 又唔洗成日沖涼<br />\n基本上 佢哋會自己搞掂自己 <br />\n問題係 你要接受到貓嘅性格<br />\n有啲人養落咗先發現自己唔鍾意貓<br />\n貓未必會聽你教 就算知道唔做得都懶理你<br />\n佢想搵你玩先會搵你 唔好旨意佢哋會好似狗咁跟出跟入 更加唔好講你嗌佢個名就跑到你面前<br />\n如果你係好著重同寵物之間嘅羈絆<br />\n貓未必適合 貓同狗都幾大分別<br />\n<br />\n我有個養貓嘅朋友講 隻貓無話特別愛邊位屋企人<br />\n純粹喺度一齊住 你哋比嘢我食 同我玩吓嘅人<br />\n唔同狗 你走咗去就傻傻企喺原地等你<br />\n試過我帶隻狗 佢帶隻貓 一齊出嚟玩<br />\n我原本都想養埋貓 但對比下 真係睇到個分別<br />\n我自己都係比較偏向狗嗰個感情"},{"pid":"2a6ffcf0c2c903a7ff8436ecb44807aeb79d42d6","tid":1048374,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"410b34e095ab776e0267e8eba1d4d9f198a025db","tid":1048374,"uid":187363,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:21:16.000Z","msg":"放過佢啦<br />\n你想養嗰種動物係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:40:02.000Z","msg":"但都希望樓主係願意去了解一下貓<br />\n而唔好因為咁樣而棄養佢"},{"pid":"47271c03514ef26d17b995914d5aed8160423dff","tid":1048374,"uid":187363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a6ffcf0c2c903a7ff8436ecb44807aeb79d42d6","tid":1048374,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"410b34e095ab776e0267e8eba1d4d9f198a025db","tid":1048374,"uid":187363,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:21:16.000Z","msg":"放過佢啦<br />\n你想養嗰種動物係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:40:02.000Z","msg":"但都希望樓主係願意去了解一下貓<br />\n而唔好因為咁樣而棄養佢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:43:09.000Z","msg":"要了解一早了解左<br />\n養左先黎上網問  點解唔係養之前一早了解先 有個心理準備"},{"pid":"35f1c6b1ca9cc16449c2267f201136e4fea3eccf","tid":1048374,"uid":187363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47271c03514ef26d17b995914d5aed8160423dff","tid":1048374,"uid":187363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a6ffcf0c2c903a7ff8436ecb44807aeb79d42d6","tid":1048374,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"410b34e095ab776e0267e8eba1d4d9f198a025db","tid":1048374,"uid":187363,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:21:16.000Z","msg":"放過佢啦<br />\n你想養嗰種動物係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:40:02.000Z","msg":"但都希望樓主係願意去了解一下貓<br />\n而唔好因為咁樣而棄養佢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:43:09.000Z","msg":"要了解一早了解左<br />\n養左先黎上網問  點解唔係養之前一早了解先 有個心理準備"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:43:49.000Z","msg":"唔要俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我中意布偶"},{"pid":"b6038334a7573d9ffcde52ee04b62d62a691b0f7","tid":1048374,"uid":11774,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"47271c03514ef26d17b995914d5aed8160423dff","tid":1048374,"uid":187363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a6ffcf0c2c903a7ff8436ecb44807aeb79d42d6","tid":1048374,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"410b34e095ab776e0267e8eba1d4d9f198a025db","tid":1048374,"uid":187363,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:21:16.000Z","msg":"放過佢啦<br />\n你想養嗰種動物係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:40:02.000Z","msg":"但都希望樓主係願意去了解一下貓<br />\n而唔好因為咁樣而棄養佢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:43:09.000Z","msg":"要了解一早了解左<br />\n養左先黎上網問  點解唔係養之前一早了解先 有個心理準備"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:55:31.000Z","msg":"咁起碼都叫有心問呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者人哋養前有了解過呢<br />\n<br />\n我養狗前都睇咗幾本書 但睇書比實際做容易<br />\n睇書會覺得好簡單啫嘛<br />\n點樣令佢喺陌生環境渡過頭嗰個星期<br />\n又要令佢夜晚唔會因為不安而叫<br />\n真係要過來人教路㗎<br />\n<br />\n我都聽人講過 布偶最痴人<br />\n可能咁樣 樓主先揀布偶 以為會比較好<br />\n點都好過啲人一句唔鍾意就唔要呀"},{"pid":"7e4cde40aad4414c1a676688110dc7ea1fad1870","tid":1048374,"uid":42449,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T16:00:06.000Z","msg":"咁多位，我冇棄養之意，而且我地都想俾最好ge 野佢，先對佢嚴d, e.g. 改晒佢d 飲食習慣，改食好d ge 糧etc.<br />\n<br />\n同埋聽親好多布偶好痴人的，而且佢第一日入屋同而家好大落差，<br />\n所以先而家先問，重點係有咩方法修補關係。<br />\n如果係本性如此，點解會同第一日咁大落差姐。"},{"pid":"0852f1639e63cd81d7a49bb946d55fd02bb439b7","tid":104837